---
title: Mediterranean-Inspired Chicken Thigh and Rice with Tomato-Feta Salsa
description: Lemon pepper-dusted chicken thighs are cooked together with the rice in this Mediterranean-inspired dish, which helps to ensure they come out tender and full of flavour. A bright and briny tomato-feta salsa is served alongside to add freshness to every savoury bite.
